## Limitations

The analysis is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or recent scholarly debates on the topic. Additionally, the focus was primarily on the geopolitical and institutional impacts, potentially overlooking cultural or economic dimensions. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of World War II's lasting effects on international relations.